room_title: Escape room "Steampunk Airship" by Portland Escape Rooms in Portland
room_address: 10700 SW Beaverton-Hillsdale Hwy, Suite 118 Beaverton OR 97005
room_description: Strap on your goggles and prepare for adventure as we transport you to another world of steam and gears! You and your team will become the crew of the Undaunted, a famous airship that stands against the devious Allied Industry Corps. Can you thwart the Corps and fly the Undaunted to safety in this new choose-your-own-adventure style escape experience, or will you fall from the sky?
